    "monster5900": "<h1 class=monster>Monkey<br><span class=type>Tiny natural beast</span><br><span class=level>Level 1 Minion Skirmisher<span class=xp> XP 0</span></span></h1><table class=bodytable><tr><td><b>HP</b> 1; a missed attack never damages a minion.<td class=rightalign><b>Initiative</b> +5<tr><td><b>AC</b> 14, <b>Fortitude</b> 10, <b>Reflex</b> 12, <b>Will</b> 10 ; add your level to each defense<td class=rightalign><b>Perception</b>+0<tr><td><b>Speed</b> 6, climb 6<td class=rightalign><tr><td colspan=2></table><h2>Traits</h2><p class='flavor alt'> <b>Nimble Fingers</b> </p><p class=flavorIndent>While within 10 squares of the monkey, the monkey's master can take a standard action to command it to make a Thievery check to pick a pocket as a free action, using the master's Thievery modifier with a +2 bonus.</p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Skills</b> Acrobatics +8<br> <b>Str</b> 5 (-3)                <b>Dex</b> 17 (+3)                <b>Wis</b> 10 (0)<br><b>Con</b> 12 (+1)                <b>Int</b> 4 (-3)                <b>Cha</b> 13 (+1)</p><p class=flavor><b>Alignment</b> Unaligned       <b> Languages</b> -<br>Update (6/28/2011)<br>Changed to match July update.<br><br></p><p class=publishedIn>Published in Dragon Magazine 399.</p>",
