    "monster200": "<h1 class=monster>Fey Panther<br><span class=type>Medium fey beast </span><br><span class=level>Level 4 Skirmisher<span class=xp> XP 175</span></span> </h1> <p class=flavor><b>Initiative</b> +8        <b>Senses</b> Perception +8; low-light vision<br><b>HP</b> 54; <b>Bloodied</b> 27<br><b>AC</b> 18; <b>Fortitude</b> 16, <b>Reflex</b> 18, <b>Will</b> 15<br><b>Speed</b> 8, climb 6</p><p class='flavor alt'>(⚔) <b>Bite</b> (standard, at-will) </p><p class=flavorIndent>+9 vs AC; 1d6+4 damage, and the fey panther shifts 1 square. </p><p class='flavor alt'> <b>Charging Pounce</b></p><p class=flavorIndent>When the fey panther charges, it deals an extra 1d6 damage and knocks the target prone.</p><p class='flavor alt'> <b>Fey Step</b> (move; encounter) ✦ <b>Teleportation</b></p><p class=flavorIndent>The fey panther can teleport 5 squares.</p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Alignment</b> Unaligned       <b> Languages</b> -<br><b>Skills</b> Stealth +11<br><b>Str</b> 14 (+4)      <b>Dex</b> 18 (+6)      <b>Wis</b> 13 (+3)<br><b>Con</b> 14 (+4)      <b>Int</b> 2 (-2)      <b>Cha</b> 11 (+2)</p><br><p class=publishedIn>Published in Monster Manual, page(s) 213, Dungeon Magazine 178, page(s) 41.</p>",
